{full_outline}

YOUR CHAPTER OUTLINE:
Chapter {chapter_number} of {total_chapters}: {chapter_title}
Summary: {chapter_summary}
Main key data: {main_key_data}
Event description: {event_description}
Event cause (WHY this event happens): {event_cause}
Scene open: {scene_open}
Scene action: {scene_action}
Scene close: {scene_close}
Sub key data (background texture — weave into scenes, do NOT develop as standalone scenes): {sub_key_data}
Chapter structure: {chapter_structure}
Opening style: {opening_style}
Closing type: {closing_type}
Emotional beat: {emotional_beat}
